snippet.title: POSITRON X - OFFICIAL EA RELEASE
snippet.description:
PositronX is a Rogue-lite First Person Shooter that emphasizes on strategic fast paced combat, creative time and movement mechanics and detailed graphical quality, packed into a highly re-playable experience. 

Check our site and consider wishlist us for further updates or buy the game if you feel is already right up your alley.
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/529970/PositronX
Main Site - http://www.scorpiusstudios.com/positron
